cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using these metadata."
title: "msptc: A configuration-driven simulation core for molten-salt parabolic-trough CSP"
abstract: >-
  Configuration-driven Python simulation core for parabolic-trough concentrating
  solar power with molten salt, covering analytical error-cone optics, Forristall
  HCE thermodynamics, collector loop, thermal storage and power block, altitude-
  dependent air properties, freeze protection, exergy, and techno-economic and
  market-value analysis.
type: software
authors:
